				<font face="verdana" size="3" color="white"><a name="2">Crushbone Aid Station on Firiona Vie</a></font><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="white">
				<b><a href="mailto:korenth@everlore.com" class="link">Korenth</b></a>
				[5/6/2002-11:02:29 AM]</font>
				&nbsp;
				
				<a href="Comments.asp?ID=573937" class="link"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Comments[2]</font></a>
				
				<p>
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="white"><blockquote>
  <p>Aleyla Stormynytes writes:</p>
  <blockquote>
    <font color=beige><p>On Saturday, May 11th, the Kelethin Legions will be puting on an Aid 
    Station within Crushbone. All of you young adventurers, the Legions are here 
    to help thee rid our Faydark of these vile beings!<br>
    <br>
    From 12 pm - 1 pm pst (3 - 5 pm est) Kelethin Legions members will be inside 
    the tunnel to Crushbone and other strategic places to help out those that 
    venture into the orc lands.<br>
    Be well young ones, and be safe.<br>
    <br>
    Aleyla Stormynytes<br>
    Ambassador of the Kelethin Legions<br>
    High Sorceress of Firiona Vie</p></font>
